{"tid":2349044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲17萬網友多謝勁贏華仔！千嬅：我帶娛樂畀佢哋！","createTime":"2021-01-01T08:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T09:06:04.000Z","uid":58552,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d0953cafb78969614035771ef1011fb2c2f96d","tid":2349044,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:40:58.000Z","msg":"由雅虎網站（Yahoo!）舉辦的「好想多謝嘅公眾人物」投票選舉昨日公布結果，今年人氣急升的<span class=\"red\">楊千嬅</span>獲十七萬票名列榜首，比第二名的<span class=\"red\">劉德華</span>多十一萬票，曾奪得「青少年最崇拜偶像」第一名的陳慧琳則排第三。<br />\n<br />\n雅虎網站（Yahoo!）在今年八月底開始，展開「好想多謝嘅香港人」網上投票活動，讓網友表揚一些一直在身邊支持鼓勵及啟發自己的人物，為期一個月。在逾四十萬的選票當中，楊千嬅以十七萬多的高票數成為「好想多謝嘅公眾人物」組別首位，而曾是「青少年最崇拜偶像」的陳慧琳（Kelly），今次則獲得四萬零五百七十六票，屈居第三，第二位的是得六萬零一十票的劉德華。除了藝人外，陳方安生、<span class=\"red\">董建華</span>及李麗珊亦入選十大。<br />\n<br />\n努力做好本份 <br />\n楊千嬅昨日接受電話訪問，對於網友為何想感謝她，千嬅說：「其實我一直都努力做好一個歌手同演員嘅本份，或者佢哋覺得我真係帶到娛樂畀佢哋啩，反而我好想多謝投我票嘅人，多謝佢哋欣賞同埋認同我，總之就多謝晒啦。」 <br />\n<br />\nKelly屈居千嬅之後，不過她毫不介意，Kelly昨日說：「唔緊要啦，有人多謝我咪好囉，一二三四位都冇所謂。」問Kelly會否覺得被千嬅威脅？她說：「多謝千嬅，多謝全部人啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2002年9月25日</span><br />\n<br />\n睇返舊時報紙新聞，真係認真過癮，呢班友幾咁辜負香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20020925/URDUAMV35XXNYSHV7MLNCPWOQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20020925%2FURDUAMV35XXNYSHV7MLNCPWOQI%2F&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=78d6d854\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20020925%2FURDUAMV35XXNYSHV7MLNCPWOQI%2F&h=82eb5e21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20020925/URDUAMV35XXNYSHV7MLNCPWOQI/</a>"},{"pid":"fd63986c21c3888b9fe6b279e84b89f4d8fce779","tid":2349044,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"多謝楊千嬅同劉德華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb83f3f0d4c584ac1c300b88ed4a2b65aa5e9136","tid":2349044,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"仲有人用yahoo嫁咩"},{"pid":"2678fd0f816cb5a7b5c1b7a1f74b86d36eed94ff","tid":2349044,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦過撚曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6404331bfaa71700ebeee4920b1a55f88f178e8f","tid":2349044,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"廿年都黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecc9814d85e3e18f3a6239d39580623e3222215","tid":2349044,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2678fd0f816cb5a7b5c1b7a1f74b86d36eed94ff","tid":2349044,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦過撚曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"而家佢地嘅target 都唔係香港人<br />\n支國人當佢地係寶就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src